        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Microsoft：网上内容有如「免费软件」　抓取用来训练 AI 模型并无问题</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/microsoft-ai-2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-ai-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/microsoft-ai-2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 12:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247041</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>大型语言模型训练时总会使用极大量的数据，抓取网上内容进行训练就成为了备受争议的行为。Microsoft AI 总裁 Mustafa Suleyman 最近就表示，个人在网上发布的内容本质上是「免费软件」，任何人都可以拿来复制甚至再创作。<br /><span id="more-1247041"></span></p><p>Microsoft AI 总裁 Mustafa Suleyman 认为，网上的内容大致分为个人发布和受公司版权保护两种，前者自 1990 年代以来，就被视为可以「合理使用」，任何人都可以复制和再创作。另外一部分则是那些明确声明「不得抓取」的网站或出版商的内容。Suleyman 表示，这属于灰色地带，需要透过法庭来解决。Suleyman 预测，资讯经济学即将发生根本性变革，知识生产的边际成本将降至零。这意味著，大量由用户贡献的「免费」内容，反而需要用户付费给大财团才能使用。</p><p>不过这个言论却在现时的争议上火上加油，非牟利组织调查报导中心 (Center for Investigative Reporting) 就在不久后起诉 OpenAI 和其最大投资者 Microsoft，指控他们未经许可使用该非营利新闻机构的内容且未提供补偿。而此前已有多家报社和作家因类似原因对 OpenAI 和 Microsoft 提起诉讼。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.theregister.com/2024/06/28/microsoft_ceo_ai/">The Register</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/apple-openai-google-gemini/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传 Apple 为保险两边下注   iOS 18 或同时采用 OpenAI、Google 人工智能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/microsoft-ai-2/ai/">Microsoft：网上内容有如「免费软件」　抓取用来训练 AI 模型并无问题</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/microsoft-ai-2/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Google 全新大语言模型 Gemma 2  270 亿参数能在高阶电脑上运行</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/gemma-2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gemma-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/gemma-2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 10:00:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gemma 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247037</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>Google 发布最新大规模语言模型 Gemma 2，此模型提供 90 亿及 270 亿参数两个版本。同时 Google 也更新了开发者专用的 Gemini 1.5 Pro，扩大了其功能与应用范围。</p><p>Gemma 2 是在先前模型的基础上改进而来，提供了更高效的推理能力并显著提升了安全性。270 亿参数的 Gemma 2，能够在单一的 Google Cloud TPU 主机或 NVIDIA 的高阶 GPU 上高效执行，其性能超越了市场上同类型的其他大规模模型。90 亿参数版本则在性能上超越了 Meta 的 Llama 3 以及其他同等规模的模型，提供类别最佳的性能。</p><p>此外 Google 还对 Gemini 1.5 Pro 进行了重要更新，现在该模型支援高达 200 万的 token 上下文窗口，并具备执行代码的能力。这一更新使得开发者能够在不连接网路的环境中试验 Python 代码，进一步增强了模型的应用灵活性与安全性。</p><p>Gemma 2 工具可应用于高性能游戏笔记型电脑和高阶桌面电脑，亦能在云端环境中实现成本效益高的运行，使各类规模的企业均能根据预算实施 AI 解决方案。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://blog.google/technology/developers/google-gemma-2/">Google</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/gemma-2/ai/">Google 全新大语言模型 Gemma 2  270 亿参数能在高阶电脑上运行</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/gemma-2/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】Philips 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动咖啡机开箱评测　全自动操控简单 + 咖啡相对淡味</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/philips-2200-lattego-coffee-machine-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=philips-2200-lattego-coffee-machine-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/philips-2200-lattego-coffee-machine-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 09:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2200 LatteGo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EP230/10]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[philips]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1246195</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>每个星期，Edward 都为大家带来不少 3C 产品的各项深入评测。去到周末，不如来些轻松点的产品。最近朋友家中就入手了 Philips 最新推出的 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动咖啡机，笔者本身就对咖啡冲调十分有兴趣，知道朋友入手了这部新机，自然立即去体验一下。现在就让笔者为大家带来此机的开箱评测吧。</p><h2>2200 系列 Latte Go 开箱直击</h2><p>同样地，在为大家分享 Philips 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动咖啡机的使用体验前，先让笔者为 unwire.hk 读者们带来它的开箱直击吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 Philips 最新推出的 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动意式咖啡机了。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246223" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03601-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03601-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03601.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒上写著它设有香味萃取装置，可以将咖啡豆内的香气尽量弄出来，令咖啡更香。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03598-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03598-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03598.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，它亦可以制作三种咖啡：Espresso 浓缩咖啡、Coffee 一般咖啡及 Cappuccino 泡沫咖啡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03603-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03603-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03603.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03604-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03604-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03604.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03606-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03606-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03606.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开箱了！大家可以见到包装十分简单，最顶层已经见到所有配件，包括隔水盖、说明书 ssss、咖啡粉匙、试水纸及一支用于保养的胶。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03607-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03607-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03607.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246230" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03608-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03608-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03608.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再下方就是咖啡机主体了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03610-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03610-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03610.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，由于笔者朋友选购的是较高阶的 2200 系列，所以除了附送 LatteGo 奶泡系统外，亦附送 AquaClean 过滤系统，无需另购。</p><h2>型格悭位黑色机身安装方便</h2><p>今次 Philips 推出的 2200 系列 Latte Go 全自动咖啡机，采用近乎全黑色的机身设计，边位加入少许银边，整体设计颇为专业及有型。另外，它的体积只是 246 x 371 x 433mm，相对一般家用咖啡机来说算是颇为细部，颇为悭位，十分适合居住环境较狭小的香港家居使用。此外，安装上亦十分简单：只要放入咖啡萃取装置，之后加水并放入水箱，再在机顶放入咖啡豆，就可以开始冲调咖啡了。它亦加入了 LatteGo 奶泡系统，方便用家以全自动方式制作 cappuccino 泡沫咖啡，可说是「麻雀虽小五脏俱全」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246234" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03611-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03611-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03611.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 Philips 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动意式咖啡机的真身，大家可以见到它采用较高身及窄身的设计，而且采用黑色为主体，配以银色边位的型格设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246235" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03631-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03631-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03631.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这种高窄身的设计，十分适合居住环境较狭小的香港家居使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03640-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03640-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03640.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身正面上方为操控板。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246236" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03616-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03616-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03616.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而下方中间为出啡位，而左方则是用于安装打奶泡的 LatteGo 系统，平常亦可用来输出热水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246239" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03618-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03618-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03618.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下方则设有水槽，可以用于储存排出来的废水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246240" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03617-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03617-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03617.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而水槽内红色的为水满提示器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246241" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03620-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03620-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03620.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246242" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03621-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03621-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03621.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机身右侧就是 1.8L 水箱，采用前拉式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246244" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03626-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03626-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03626.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03628-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03628-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03628.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03629-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03629-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246247" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03630-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03630-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03630.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而上图这个就是整部全自动咖啡机的「灵魂」：香味萃取装置，可以将研磨后的咖啡豆的香气尽量萃取出来，令冲调出来的咖啡更香。官方建议这个装置需要每星期清洁一次，而方法十分简单：用清水冲洗，之后风干即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03622-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03622-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03622.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03624-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03624-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03624.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲只要将香味萃取装置放进机内，之后关上闸门，再装上水箱，就可以使用了。</p><h2>操作简单「傻瓜」都识冲</h2><p>至于操作方面亦十分简单，作为一部全自动的意式咖啡机，基本上只要已放入咖啡豆及水，再将杯放在出啡口，之后按下想冲调的咖啡种类按键，就可以坐定定等咖啡冲好然后享受了，那种「傻瓜机」操作模式基本上任何人都可以轻易上手。即使要冲调泡沫咖啡，同样亦只需要插上加入了鲜奶的 LatteGo 奶泡系统，同样可以很快冲好一杯拥有绵密奶泡的泡沫咖啡，十分适合一些对咖啡质素有一定要求，但又无时间慢慢手动冲调的用家使用。另一个笔者觉得设计得十分体贴的地方，就是它的出啡位高度是可以调校的，换言之无论用家的杯是大是细，也不会担心冲出来的咖啡会溅出杯外弄污枱面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03632-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03632-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03632.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲操作方面亦十分简单，只要大家将水箱装满水。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1246252 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_193412-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_193412-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_193412.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲之后将咖啡豆放于豆箱内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03612-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03612-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03612.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再透过面板选择想冲调的咖啡种类即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246254" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03636-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03636-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03636.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03638-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03638-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03638.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲像笔者想冲调普通咖啡，只要按一下 Coffee 按键，再将杯放在出啡口下，之后再按下最右方的按键，冲调过程就会开始。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03639-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03639-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03639.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲出啡位亦设有升降系统，如果使用细杯（例如：Espresso 杯），可以将它按下，这样咖啡就不会容易溅出杯外。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154632-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154632-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154632.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154818-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154818-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154818.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果要冲调泡沫咖啡，就装上 LatteGo 奶泡系统，之后将牛奶倒进杯内（当然建议使用全脂牛奶），之后放杯，再按下面板上的 Cappuccino，再按下冲调键（最右方的按键）即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154853-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154853-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154853.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154918-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154918-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_154918.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲之后系统会将蒸气快速加进奶泡系统，除了加热牛奶外，亦会透过蒸气压力从 LatteGo 底部的微孔将牛奶吸气，再透过官方声称的旋风奶泡技术混合牛奶及蒸气，再打出奶泡，之后再倒进杯内。完成倒奶过程度，再将咖啡加入牛奶中，就可以制成一杯泡沫咖啡了，整个过程只需 2 分钟左右，十分快。</p><h2>材料支援度高不难打理</h2><p>另外，这部咖啡机在管理上亦十分方便，奶基本上可按需要才加入，而咖啡豆亦只需要倒进机顶拥有 AromaSeal 香气封盖功能的储豆箱即可，每次制作咖啡时系统才会以咖啡豆新鲜研磨出咖啡粉再进行冲调，保持新鲜效果及不会让咖啡豆的香味流走。当然，在储豆箱前方亦设有细小的阀门，打开后就可以将已磨好的咖啡粉放进去，同样可以用于冲调咖啡。至于水方面，前拉式的水箱拉出及安装都十分方便，而且怕烦的用家，亦可装上 AquaClean 过滤系统，有了它大家只需要直接从水喉取水（最好先经过滤，但没有过滤问题亦不大）即可，无需事先煲滚消毒，十分方便。而且咖啡冲调完成后，咖啡渣会跌进机内的收藏槽，定时清理就可以了，打理上十分轻松。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03613-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03613-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03613.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲咖啡豆箱设有 AromaSeal 香气封盖功能，可以将咖啡豆香气有效保存在豆箱内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03614-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03614-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03614.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而豆箱前方设有一个小阀门，方便用家使用已研磨好的咖啡粉冲调咖啡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03619-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03619-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机内亦设有收藏咖啡豆渣的小盒，满了面板会见到指示灯亮起，提示用家需要清洁。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03633-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03633-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03633.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，如果在水箱加入了 AquaClean 过滤系统，用家只需放入水喉水已可冲调咖啡，无需放凉滚水，更加方便。</p><h2>咖啡偏淡味建议自行调校</h2><p>至于冲调出来的效果，事先声明，笔者并非专业的咖啡冲调师或品评师，未能为大家提供十分专业的咖啡饮用后感，只能按个人意见表达。Edward 本人平时饮开的咖啡是比较深焙、浓味，而预设的研磨档次及冲调设定，笔者觉得会令咖啡豆的香味「未出尽」，感觉偏淡味一点。当然，对于习惯享受啡味较淡的用家来说，这个设定可能会比较适合，但笔者个人会选择将研磨档次设定在 10 档左右（粗研磨），再将香味等级调至最高的第三级，出来的咖啡就比较适当个人口味了。当然，这部咖啡机有一个十分好的设计，就是可以将用家的冲调喜好储存下来，下次只要按下咖啡种类，就会按之前的设定冲调咖啡，不用每次均重新设定，十分体贴。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1246274 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_194855-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_194855-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240612_194855.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155004-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155004-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155004.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲冲调效果方面，笔者先以预设设定冲调，发现出来的香味确实十分浓郁，但味道偏淡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03615-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03615-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03615.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果你像笔者一样喜欢较浓味的咖啡，可以先将研磨度调至粗研磨效果，大约数值 10 就足够了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155337-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155337-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155337.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲之后再将香味设定调至最高的第三级。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155532-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155532-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_20240622_155532-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这样出来的咖啡就会比较浓味一点。另外，大家可以见到它的香味萃取系统做得十分不错，将咖啡豆内的油层亦冲出来，令咖啡更加香。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_31449"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GEyAlhaRY9w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲最后附上官方的使用说明影片让大家参考。</p><h2>总结：冲调靓啡简简单单无烦恼</h2><p>总括而言，今次 Philips 新推出的 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动咖啡机，可说是将安装、冲调、清洗打理各方面的步骤简单至近乎极致，令大家可以无需任何技巧，只需要买回自己喜欢的咖啡豆，就可以冲调出一杯口感不错的咖啡，对于生活繁忙的都市人来说，确实是最悭钱可以享受靓啡的方案。当然，代价就是这部全自动咖啡机绝对不便宜，虽然最近在做大特价，也要索价近 $5,000，但一部功能齐全的全自动咖啡机其实一向也不「便宜」，这个价位笔者觉得还算合理。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/dsc03597-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/29/philips-2200-lattego-coffee-machine-review/review-2/">【评测】Philips 2200 系列 LatteGo 全自动咖啡机开箱评测　全自动操控简单 + 咖啡相对淡味</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
